{"tid":1002841,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"少男記憶全毀！「早安」前女神膨脹兩size","createTime":"2019-01-31T08:30:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-31T10:28:18.000Z","uid":32511,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"8131be8214ece139b2aa37391c663c7e312cad5a","tid":1002841,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T08:30:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LCGkkEM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLCGkkEM.jpg&h=06210e91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「早安少女組」前成員石川梨華是「早安」全盛時期的人氣女神之一，當時擄獲大批少男的心。前年下嫁小2歲日本職棒埼玉西武獅隊投手野上亮磨後，去年升格當媽。近日，石川梨華粉絲們為她舉辦生日會慶祝34歲，卻見她變成麵包臉，身材發福與昔日纖瘦模樣判若兩人，不少網友看到當年的偶像變成圓滾滾的大媽，直呼少年美好回憶都碎了。<br />\n<br />\n另一位幸福肥的還有「早安」前隊長藤本美貴，和諧星庄司智春結婚近10年，如今育有一子一女的藤本明顯發福，比起偶像時代的體型似乎加大了兩個size，日前亮相節目時肚子明顯凸起，更被懷疑有第三胎。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/urm046v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Furm046v.jpg&h=294185c8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"382c67c1ebf262118d530a01e4306e907ba0144c","tid":1002841,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T08:37:02.000Z","msg":"脹爆肉丸"},{"pid":"382cad16771533a2fbe1e962950b6e09028b4e5d","tid":1002841,"uid":73,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T08:37:04.000Z","msg":"仲正左!"},{"pid":"3ed9338ef3893f39f172bb2f0ee042519d9fb66f","tid":1002841,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T08:38:29.000Z","msg":"有肉地<br />\n正呀"},{"pid":"3fca54f6383b222be8a299137a2f41fa05d38985","tid":1002841,"uid":136645,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T08:41:24.000Z","msg":"第一張圖係近照?  咁都叫差"},{"pid":"1851a9c81d9945bfee3006aa1819f4f961175304","tid":1002841,"uid":42283,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T08:48:15.000Z","msg":"第一張都好好睇喎"},{"pid":"8b772b5d0564cae44a71024b82c57102187b9e39","tid":1002841,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3fca54f6383b222be8